author: jwross
msg: ARIES-825: Multiple changes.
(1) Fixed issue in itests where a resolved subsystem was being stopped.
(2) Fixed exact version range check for composites.
(3) Default value for versions in composites is [0.0,0.0].
(4) Fixed issue in ClauseTokenizer where quotes were not being re-inserted.
(5) Fixed issue in ClauseTokenizer where empty strings were being added.
(6) VersionRangeAttribute now returns value in quotes.
(7) Allow for null repositories when computing dependencies.
(8) Don't create empty export policies on regions.
(9) Detect stale subsystem references when uninstalling.
(10) Fixed persistence autostart setting issues.
(11) Only remove region on install failures if subsystem is scoped.
(12) Fixed issue where subsystem directory was not getting cleaned up on install failure because error occurred before participant was added to coordination.
